{"tid":720205,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"支股市場蒸發14兆","createTime":"2018-06-27T17:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T18:04:23.000Z","uid":159798,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e194c97250dc48c40dbba7f2d02c58e2b4692ca","tid":720205,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:58:44.000Z","msg":"愛康健模式：<br />\n假設14兆有1%去左買港樓，樓價升幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/27/bfCE0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2FbfCE0B.png&h=6dab3b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著中美貿易戰逐步升級，市場對大陸是否有足夠能力與美國打貿易戰日益擔心，大陸股市近日跌跌不休，雖然中共央行前日（24日）降準放水救市，但昨日上證指數收盤再下跌0.5%，使該指數自今年一月以來已下跌超過20%，正式進入熊市。在岸人民幣兌美元收市則創半年低位，報6.556兌1美元，較上日跌320點子，連跌4個交易日。人民幣持續貶值，衝擊航運、原物料、銀行類股股價；房地產類股也受官方政策收緊影響，集體暴跌。"},{"pid":"7ca33df8877a5b00fe14c39fd37ab31c1c83662d","tid":720205,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9f5a880b350917db873c819897e09adca042f2","tid":720205,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"連登三燈未出手姐 定d黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}